data.description: First-time homeowner, investor or if you simply just want a worry-free property with low maintenance, look no further!! Low monthly HOA fees that cover all the worries of exterior insurance, yard maintenance, and trash.  This well-kept 3-bedroom, 2 full bath is in the Tuloso Midway school district. Walk into an open floor plan with a spacious kitchen and great size rooms.  This property includes your own private patio, perfect for your morning coffee!  The neighborhood has amazing amenities close by and is located right within walking distance from Tuloso Primary School. Owner installed a new garbage disposal, new water heater, and a new A/C unit in 2022. Don’t wait to schedule a showing today before this opportunity is gone!!
